<body>
  <script>
    const dataset = [
                  [ 34,    78 ],
                  [ 109,   280 ],
                  [ 310,   120 ],
                  [ 79,    411 ],
                  [ 420,   220 ],
                  [ 233,   145 ],
                  [ 333,   96 ],
                  [ 222,   333 ],
                  [ 78,    320 ],
                  [ 21,    123 ]
                ];
    
    
    const w = 500;
    const h = 500;
    
    const svg = d3.select("body")
                  .append("svg")
                  .attr("width", w)
                  .attr("height", h);
    
    svg.selectAll("circle")
       .data(dataset)
       .enter()
       .append("circle")
       .attr("cx", (d, i) => d[0])
       .attr("cy", (d, i) => h - d[1])
       .attr("r", 5);
    
    svg.selectAll("text")
       .data(dataset)
       .enter()
       .append("text")
       // Add your code below this line
       .text((d, i) => d[0] + ', ' + d[1])
       .attr("x", (d, i) => d[0] + 5)
       .attr("y", (d, i) => h - d[1])
       // Add your code above this line
  </script>
</body>
